#  Binance Futures Trading Bot (Testnet)

A Python-based CLI trading bot that interacts with the Binance Futures Testnet API to place MARKET and LIMIT orders with proper logging, validation, and structured architecture.

---

##  Features

- Place MARKET and LIMIT orders (USDT-M Futures Testnet)
- CLI-based user input system
- Live price fetch before placing order
- Structured modular architecture
- Input validation system
- Logging of requests, responses, and errors
- Clean terminal UI with colored output

