## ️ Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/ishansamanta/trading-bot
cd trading-bot
```
## 2. Install Dependencies
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```
## 3. Create .env file
```bash
API_KEY=your_testnet_api_key
API_SECRET=your_testnet_secret_key
```
## 4. Get Binance Testnet API Keys
Go to Binance Futures Testnet
Generate API Key and Secret
Add them in .env

## 5. How to Run
Start the bot:
```bash
python cli.py
```